(# EEG Seizure Detection Model Report \(CHB-MIT, 16x256\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(## Abstract) Tj
0 -14 Td
(This report summarizes the EEG seizure detection pipeline and model experiments on CHB-MIT using) Tj
0 -14 Td
(1-second windows \(`16 channels x 256 samples`\). We compared CNN and EEGNet baselines plus improved) Tj
0 -14 Td
(variants. The processed dataset produced subject-independent train/val/test tensors with balancing) Tj
0 -14 Td
(to 30% seizure in each split. In captured runs, `cnn_benchmark` and `eegnet` achieved similar final) Tj
0 -14 Td
(test F1 \(~0.528\), while `cnn_improved` and `eegnet_improved` showed different precision-recall) Tj
0 -14 Td
(tradeoffs. AUROC/AUPRC were `nan` in logs and should be recomputed after fixing metric) Tj
0 -14 Td
(dependency/runtime.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
