(## 6. Interpretation) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `cnn_benchmark` and `eegnet` delivered similar final F1, but with very different operating) Tj
0 -14 Td
(profiles.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `eegnet` achieved highest recall, but low specificity \(more false positives\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `cnn_benchmark` gave better specificity and better overall balance.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `cnn_improved` underperformed `cnn_benchmark` in this run \(lower F1 and accuracy\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `eegnet_improved` improved over `cnn_improved` F1, but did not exceed `cnn_benchmark`/`eegnet`) Tj
0 -14 Td
(baseline F1 in captured runs.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
